---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { getPageMeta } from "../utils/meta";

const { title, description, canonical } = getPageMeta(Astro.site, {
  title: "About",
  description: "How Top10Maison ranks products using review data, consistent criteria, and editorial review.",
  path: "/about/"
});
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">About Top10Maison</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">
          Top10Maison publishes top lists and buying guidance to help you choose faster for your home.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">
          We focus on clear, practical comparisons built from publicly available product information, review data,
          and availability. Each list follows a consistent set of criteria so rankings stay fair and repeatable
          across categories.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">
          Our goal is simple: to publish shortlists that reflect everyday household needs, without unnecessary
          complexity or hype.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Methodology</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/70">
          Rankings are created using the same framework across all categories. We do not perform hands-on testing.
          Instead, we rely on consistent evaluation factors to compare products on equal footing.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">Factors may include:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-sm text-ink/70">
          <li>Product specifications and intended use</li>
          <li>Review volume and overall ratings</li>
          <li>Availability and price consistency</li>
          <li>Value relative to similar products</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Editorial review</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/70">
          We use data-assisted analysis to surface review patterns and trend signals, then apply editorial review
          to finalize each shortlist. This approach helps keep comparisons grounded in real-world feedback while
          avoiding marketing-driven claims.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">
          Data helps identify patterns, and editors review each list before publication to ensure the rankings
          remain practical and easy to understand.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Affiliate disclosure</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/70">
          Some links on Top10Maison may be affiliate links, which means we may earn a commission if you make a
          purchase.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/70">
          This does not affect how products are scored, ranked, or selected. Affiliate relationships do not
          influence editorial decisions, criteria, or placement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
